Problem                                 Pattern
Find duplicate in sorted array.      Adjacent comparison
Remove duplicates                     Two pointers (slow/fast)
Two Sum                                Nested loop / HashMap
XOR unique element                     Bit manipulation

///Common LeetCode problems using HashSet
Problem                                  Why HashSet
Contains Duplicate                     Check if seen before
Happy Number                               Detect cycle
Intersection of Two Arrays              Unique common elements
Longest Consecutive Sequence             Fast existence check
Valid Sudoku                           No repetition allowed

